640700,"uid":290176,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:31:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">廢后林鄭想同習帝玩鋪勁</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:35:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MLJGb8g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMLJGb8g.jpg&h=3b3857fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6af2871b40bbacc1e305328907e718e48f39f530","tid":1640700,"uid":279236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:36:44.000Z","msg":"[為雙10感謝祭打開序幕]呢間餐廳大家一定要試下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1640686\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1640686</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0cfa7d270c9b1eba0e034b104ebefa0c86e1bd3d","tid":1640700,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:36:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">全球「和尼畫」<br />\n#XinniethePooh Challenge</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1640322/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rG1sQ5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrG1sQ5b.jpg&h=d6b3d577&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K9NvORS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK9NvORS.jpg&h=fcaaa2a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「和尼畫」挑戰<br />\n1.畫出你心中所想的維尼圖<br />\n2.留下你想對習維尼講嘅說話<br />\n3.放上ig、fb、twitter，tag #XinniethePooh<br />\n4.tag 1-3個你想佢一齊畫維尼嘅朋友<br />\n5.被tag嘅朋友一齊畫維尼，讓愛與維尼佔領地球，推到畀習維尼本人見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「Xinnie the Pooh」Challenge<br />\n1. Draw your own &quot;Xinnie the Pooh&quot;<br />\n2. Write down what do you want to tell Chairman Xi<br />\n3. Post your work on instagram, facebook and twitter with tag #Xinnie the Pooh<br />\n4. Tag up to 3 more friends to ask them draw together!<br />\n5. Those who are tagged also join to draw Xinnie the Pooh, keep drawing until Chairman Xi can see our works!!"},{"pid":"451cc1af22a7a8bc7506ad8989050ca557c8ed1b","tid":1640700,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:37:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f462b8a4545340cb39915d9cf11e46a330b3d10","tid":1640700,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:39:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4215b056bb998af368f15ea8be1633677977d467","tid":1640700,"uid":289751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5ceb406d4735d3a6fc5c1ebbd2fbe2a5e7ea557","tid":1640700,"uid":212626,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:30:34.000Z","msg":"以為佢兩個漏簽<br />\n睇嚟係真係唔認同所以唔簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:41:47.000Z","msg":"點有可能漏呀, 係唔肯簽既姐"},{"pid":"3a17597d42d792223f882034b72c2eaf7726c3d3","tid":1640700,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:44:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a13d66b6e4c53c60d6524f381ce8f9bf2a1fa2d","tid":1640700,"uid":227699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T05:55:06.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n雙普選<br />\n銷控罪<br />\n查警暴<br />\n非暴動<br />\n撤惡法"},{"pid":"8afe6979971b6dfa7010c16032d462d0e8926719","tid":1640700,"uid":242647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T06:01:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WmZieu1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWmZieu1.jpg&h=67ef6f38&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b2d7e3f1c6ed92c5956758db376d2025fa6d362a","tid":1640700,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":